data.description: This charming 3 bed, 2 bath single-family home is situated in the desirable Huguenot neighborhood, offering comfortable living with its spacious layout. The attached garage brings additional space along with a den area includes SGD's leading right out to the backyard. With a new roof, siding and new windows, all you have to do is add your personal touches to make it yours. Whether you're relaxing in the backyard, the nearby park, or exploring all the nearby amenities, this Huguenot gem is a great place to call home!
